<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix" style="display:none;">
<img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/398c3c87392fe68cea144a8e7abe2b96_200x112.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="670" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/398c3c87392fe68cea144a8e7abe2b96_r.jpg">
【高亮！图文+视频】【要丰胸的妹纸看过来！】前几天看了一个日本丰胸大师的按摩+穿戴Bra教程的视频。主要是【按摩】，看在是一大福利，所以冒着偏题的风险分享给大家。（不要拍我好嘛）号称一次见效，坚持按摩会有惊喜O(∩_∩)O为保证不忽悠大家，先上效果…

<a href="/question/19975029/answer/25842711" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>

</div>


<div class="zm-editable-content clearfix">
【高亮！图文+视频】<br>【要丰胸的妹纸看过来！】<br>前几天看了一个日本丰胸大师的按摩+穿戴Bra教程的视频。<br>主要是【按摩】，看在是一大福利，所以冒着偏题的风险分享给大家。（不要拍我好嘛）<br>号称一次见效，坚持按摩会有惊喜O(∩_∩)O<br>为保证不忽悠大家，先上效果图预告╮(￣▽￣")╭ （快夸我是业界良心）<br><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/398c3c87392fe68cea144a8e7abe2b96_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="670" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="670" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/398c3c87392fe68cea144a8e7abe2b96_b.jpg"><b>附视频</b>：<a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNjgzMDU5NzI4.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">日本一万两千人成功的神级丰胸按摩<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><br>因为视频比较繁琐，缩减下来就是5个步骤，截图给大家说明一下。<br>没有耐心看视频的可以看下面的步骤分解~\(≧▽≦)/~<br><br><b>Step1：由手臂下方至腋下按摩</b><br><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/e59fbabc35fae2d846016d2a5f473210_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="224" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="224" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/e59fbabc35fae2d846016d2a5f473210_b.jpg"><b>Step2：由腋下至锁骨和胸前的中间位置按摩</b><br><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/8d6154255d7cc7034b363cbae7586917_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="222" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="222" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/8d6154255d7cc7034b363cbae7586917_b.jpg"><b>Step3:由锁骨往下按捏腋下脂肪</b><br><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/5a25b27dcd989ac16b86762c70a15e5f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="221" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="221" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/5a25b27dcd989ac16b86762c70a15e5f_b.jpg"><b>Step4：双手来回从乳下方经乳头往上按摩</b><br><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/2e7a674a80dac75186bce1fd06759d83_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="223" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="223" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/2e7a674a80dac75186bce1fd06759d83_b.jpg"><b>Step5：运用大拇指由乳沟向乳头方向推按</b><br><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/24739c4790b559da9ace80b90addd112_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="229" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="229" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/24739c4790b559da9ace80b90addd112_b.jpg"><br>注：<br><b>按摩前需要涂抹身体乳/霜 或者乳，没有产品润滑是进行不了哒~</b><br><b>每个步骤反复进行几次之后再进行下一步骤~</b><br><br>ps：我也不懂日文昂，靠图像分析给大家，如果有分解不正确的地方望大家斧正么么哒~

</div>

</div>
