<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="46">

<span class="voters text">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jiang-shi-yu" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/jiang-shi-yu" target="_blank" class="zg-link" title="江诗愉">江诗愉</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$gai-gai-gai-3-85" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/gai-gai-gai-3-85" target="_blank" class="zg-link" title="盖盖盖">盖盖盖</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhou-mei-27-14" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/zhou-mei-27-14" target="_blank" class="zg-link" title="周美">周美</a></span>
