<div class="zm-item-rich-text js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="169997" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="校内内" data-entry-url="/question/19975029/answer/48671763">


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix" style="display:none;">
<img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/457b906429fba49c11dc533c380b1405_200x112.jpg" data-rawwidth="1754" data-rawheight="1241" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/457b906429fba49c11dc533c380b1405_r.jpg">
莎士比亚说：女人是被爱的，而不是被理解的。Woman is to be loved, not to be understood.我说，<b>Bra</b> is to be em<b>bra</b>ced, not to be worn.内衣不简简单单是一件衣服。它除了<b>遮挡</b>，更多的是<b>防护。</b><b>乳房</b>是没有肌肉的，只有韧带和皮肤起支撑作用。一旦受伤，所…

<a href="/question/19975029/answer/48671763" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>

</div>


<div class="zm-editable-content clearfix">
莎士比亚说：女人是被爱的，而不是被理解的。<br>Woman is to be loved, not to be understood.<br>我说，<b>Bra</b> is to be em<b>bra</b>ced, not to be worn.<br><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/457b906429fba49c11dc533c380b1405_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1754" data-rawheight="1241" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1754" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/457b906429fba49c11dc533c380b1405_r.jpg">内衣不简简单单是一件衣服。它除了</noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1754" data-rawheight="1241" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1754" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/457b906429fba49c11dc533c380b1405_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/457b906429fba49c11dc533c380b1405_b.jpg">内衣不简简单单是一件衣服。它除了<b>遮挡</b>，更多的是<b>防护。</b><br><b>乳房</b>是没有肌肉的，只有韧带和皮肤起支撑作用。一旦受伤，所造成的后果将几乎无法逆转。<br>因此，内衣是用来拥抱的，不单纯是用来穿戴的。妹子们需要选择<b>适合自己体型</b>的内衣，养成良好的穿戴习惯。

</div>

</div>
